graph TB
    subgraph "Llama Stack Server (Port 8321/TCP)"
        subgraph "llama-stack-provider-ragas"
            direction TB
            InlineProvider["Inline Provider<br/>(RagasEvaluatorInline)"]
            RemoteProvider["Remote Provider<br/>(RagasEvaluatorRemote)"]
            CompatLayer["Compatibility Layer<br/>(compat.py)"]
            Config["Configuration<br/>(config.py / constants.py)"]

            subgraph "LLM/Embedding Wrappers"
                InlineWrappers["Inline Wrappers<br/>(wrappers_inline.py)<br/>In-process API calls"]
                RemoteWrappers["Remote Wrappers<br/>(wrappers_remote.py)<br/>HTTP client calls"]
            end

            subgraph "KFP Pipeline Components"
                RetrieveData["retrieve_data_from_llama_stack<br/>(KFP Step 1)"]
                RunRagas["run_ragas_evaluation<br/>(KFP Step 2)"]
            end

            InlineProvider -->|uses| InlineWrappers
            InlineProvider -->|imports via| CompatLayer
            RemoteProvider -->|uses| RemoteWrappers
            RemoteProvider -->|submits| RetrieveData
            RemoteProvider -->|submits| RunRagas
            RetrieveData -->|feeds data to| RunRagas
            InlineProvider -->|reads| Config
            RemoteProvider -->|reads| Config
        end

        EvalAPI["/alpha/eval/* endpoints"]
        BenchmarksAPI["/benchmarks/register endpoint"]
        EvalAPI -->|dispatches to| InlineProvider
        EvalAPI -->|dispatches to| RemoteProvider
        BenchmarksAPI -->|registers with| InlineProvider
        BenchmarksAPI -->|registers with| RemoteProvider
    end

    Client[Client / User] -->|POST /alpha/eval/run-eval<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP| EvalAPI
    Client -->|POST /benchmarks/register<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP| BenchmarksAPI

    InlineWrappers -->|in-process| LlamaStackInference["Llama Stack Inference API"]
    InlineWrappers -->|in-process| LlamaStackDatasetIO["Llama Stack DatasetIO API"]

    RemoteProvider -->|HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Bearer Token| KFP["Kubeflow Pipelines API"]
    RemoteProvider -->|HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>AWS IAM| S3["S3 Storage<br/>(Results Retrieval)"]

    RunRagas -->|HTTP 8321/TCP| LlamaStackInference
    RunRagas -->|HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>AWS IAM| S3
    RetrieveData -->|HTTP 8321/TCP| LlamaStackDatasetIO

    LlamaStackInference -->|HTTP 11434/TCP| Ollama["Ollama / vLLM<br/>Inference Backend"]

    RemoteProvider -->|HTTPS 6443/TCP<br/>SA Token| K8sAPI["Kubernetes API<br/>(ConfigMap reads)"]

    style InlineProvider fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style RemoteProvider fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style InlineWrappers fill:#6bb3e0,stroke:#333
    style RemoteWrappers fill:#6bb3e0,stroke:#333
    style RetrieveData fill:#9b59b6,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style RunRagas fill:#9b59b6,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style CompatLayer fill:#95a5a6,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Config fill:#95a5a6,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style EvalAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style BenchmarksAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style KFP fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style S3 fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Ollama fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style LlamaStackInference fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style LlamaStackDatasetIO fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Client fill:#f9f9f9,stroke:#333
